OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLow cloud
OL,6,Fmaking its way back inland to affect
OL,7,Fmany places during the evening and
OL,8,Fovernight, staying dry for most with a
OL,9,Flight northeasterly breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FA cloudy morning for most
OL,12,Fplaces, but low cloud quickly retreats
OL,13,Fto the coast, resulting in a bright
OL,14,Fday for many. Feeling very warm but
OL,15,Fcooler along the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
