OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCloud on
OL,6,FFriday morning soon retreating to the
OL,7,Fcoasts. A little more cloud on
OL,8,FSaturday but staying dry. Sunday looks
OL,9,Fto be largely bright and sunny
OL,10,Fthroughout. Above average temperatures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
